b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2045,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"[Updated] Regarding Curse of Nihility and Its Effects","message":"<div><span style=\\"color: rgb(41, 105, 176);\\"><strong>[Updated <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1624612500\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><br>In a data update around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1625205600\\"><\/span>, the Skill Shift effects of the following skills will be made exempt from Curse of Nihility.<br><br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Marth&#39;s skill Fire Emblem<br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Rena&#39;s skill Roaring Furnace<br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Summer Celliera&#39;s skill Pep Talk<br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Eugene&#39;s skill Signature Tactics<br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Dragonyule Cleo&#39;s skill Starlit Gift<br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Summer Julietta&#39;s skill Vacation Vigor<br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Gauld&#39;s skill Chaotic Fissure<br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Forager Cleo&#39;s skill Camping Memories<br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Pipple&#39;s skill Puu-chu<br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Victor&#39;s skill Steel Formation<br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Joachim&#39;s skill Last Resort<br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Wu Kong&#39;s skill Ruyi Jingu Bang<br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Fleur&#39;s skill Captivating Canvas<br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Annelie&#39;s skill Stunning Display<br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Halloween Elisanne&#39;s skill Sacred Maiden<br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Sha Wujing&#39;s skill Crash Armament<br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Peony&#39;s skill Flower of Joy<br>\\u30fbThe adventurer Gala Cleo&#39;s skills Ancient Ray and Faith of the Elders<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div><hr><div><br><\/div><div>Bosses in the Rise of the Sinister Dominion quests, debuting on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1615528800\\"><\/span>, will use Curse of Nihility, which removes certain buffs on adventurers and nullifies their effects for a certain amount of time.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0What Are Buffs?<\/div><div>Buffs are stat or performance boosts granted by skills or abilities. For example, a buff may increase an adventurer&#39;s strength, defense, critical rate, or recovery potency by a certain amount. Buffs vary in effectiveness, and more than one may be active at any given time.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Buffs Affected by Curse of Nihility<\/div><div>Curse of Nihility will remove and nullify the effects of the following buffs:<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbBuffs that increase strength<\/div><div>\\u30fbBuffs that increase defense<\/div><div>\\u30fbBuffs that increase attack rate<\/div><div>\\u30fbBuffs that increase critical rate<\/div><div>\\u30fbBuffs that increase critical damage<\/div><div>\\u30fbBuffs that increase skill damage<\/div><div>\\u30fbBuffs that fill the skill gauge over time<\/div><div>\\u30fbBuffs that increase skill gauge fill rate<\/div><div>\\u30fbBuffs that upgrade or alter skill effects<\/div><div>\\u30fbBuffs that increase force strike damage<\/div><div>\\u30fbBuffs that increase force strike charge rate<\/div><div>\\u30fbBuffs that increase debuff success rate<\/div><div>\\u30fbBuffs that increase movement speed<\/div><div>\\u30fbBuffs that increase damage to enemies suffering certain conditions<\/div><div>\\u30fbBuffs from wyrmprint abilities that regenerate HP<\/div><div>\\u30fbEnergy<\/div><div>\\u30fbInspiration<\/div><div>\\u30fbLife Shield<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>\\u30fbIn the interest of preserving gameplay balance and mechanics, certain buffs that are unique to particular adventurers or dragons that grant one or more of the above effects may be exempt from Curse of Nihility.<\/div><div>\\u30fbBuffs applied by buff zones will also be removed and their effects nullified.<\/div><div>\\u30fbCurse of Nihility cannot be removed by shapeshifting.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1615442400,"prev_article_id":"1731","next_article_id":"2243","image_path":"","update_time":1624612641}}}'